  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a package hash is present for content integrity but the digital signature workflow has not yet been completed — signature field is intentionally absent pending the signing authority review cycle. Full 13-factor assessment is included. Decision: Accepted (conditional on signature completion).",
